@startuml level4_pipeline
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10

title **Level 4 — Pipeline Organization**\n//Fixed sequential order, no going back//

|#E3F2FD|Stage 1|
start
:<<Engagement Manager>>\n**Claude Haiku**\n\nDecompose question\ninto workstreams;
:Output: Analysis Plan;

|#E8F5E9|Stage 2|
:<<Market Researcher>>\n**Claude Sonnet**\n\nAnalyze market landscape;
:Output: Market Analysis;

|#FFF3E0|Stage 3|
:<<Financial Analyst>>\n**GPT-4o-mini**\n\nModel financials & projections;
:Output: Financial Analysis;

|#FFEBEE|Stage 4|
:<<Risk Analyst>>\n**Mistral Medium**\n\nIdentify & assess risks;
:Output: Risk Matrix;

|#F3E5F5|Stage 5|
:<<Strategy Consultant>>\n**Claude Opus / GPT-4**\n\nSynthesize all inputs\ninto final recommendation;
:Output: Consulting Report;

|#FFFDE7|Stage 6|
:<<Evaluator>>\n**Claude Sonnet**\n\nScore on 6-criterion rubric;
:Output: Evaluation Scorecard;
stop

note right
  **Pipeline characteristics:**
  * Strictly sequential
  * Each agent runs exactly once
  * No iteration or feedback loops
  * Fastest execution time
  * No revision capability
end note

@enduml
